Source: debathena-getcluster
Section: debathena/net
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Debian-Athena Project <debathena@mit.edu>
Build-Depends: cdbs (>= 0.4.23-1.1), autotools-dev, debhelper (>= 4.2.0), autoconf, libhesiod-dev
Standards-Version: 3.7.2

Package: debathena-getcluster
Architecture: any
Provides: getcluster
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Retrieve service cluster info from Hesiod for Athena workstations
 The getcluster program is used on all Athena workstations to find the 
 service cluster information for the workstation and writes a list of 
 environment variable assignments which can be used to initialize a 
 shell accordingly.
